rows.label: qst620204_msg0001
rows.name:
Phew, that monster must've been
preeeeetty hungry to come out
on land while we were here!

rows.label: qst620204_msg0002
rows.name:
It may have liked the taste
of veggies so much, it just
couldn't stop itself.

rows.label: qst620204_msg0003
rows.name:
Ain't nobody don't love my Energy
Aubergines, and that's a fact.

rows.label: qst620204_msg0004
rows.name:
...Oh, aye, more importantly,
I should thank you all.

rows.label: qst620204_msg0005
rows.name:
Really, up until just now
I thought yeh 'ated each
other's guts, but...

rows.label: qst620204_msg0006
rows.name:
...Seeing you fight shoulder
to shoulder like that, it were
right special, it were.

rows.label: qst620204_msg0008
rows.name:
Tokiha and the other one
are both exceptional
Blades... It is no wonder.

rows.label: qst620204_msg0009
rows.name:
I, for one, feel I've still
got a long way to go on the
path towards excellence...

rows.label: qst620204_msg0010
rows.name:
Now, now, lass. Can you please put
all that aside for t' moment and pay
attention when I'm thanking yeh?

rows.label: qst620204_msg0012
rows.name:
That, and also, getting this field back
to a usable state will take 'ard work. If
you're ever bored, feel free to 'elp.

rows.label: qst620204_msg0013
rows.name:
There'll be a reward in it for
yeh, just as there is one now.

rows.label: qst620204_msg0016
rows.name:
Anything can be a challenge
if you want it to be.

rows.label: qst620204_msg0017
rows.name: I'll see you all again soon, I'm sure.
